# Application Architecture Design

## Overview

The Smart Lender project follows a modular and scalable architecture to ensure maintainability, reusability, and future extensibility. The application is organized into separate modules for data management, machine learning, and user interaction.

The architecture follows a three-layer approach:

1. User Interface Layer
2. Backend Application Layer
3. Machine Learning Layer

This separation of concerns allows each component to be developed, tested, and maintained independently.

